2015年10月3日，在[[昆都士之戰|昆都士之戰]]中，'''[[美國空軍|美國空軍]][[空襲|空襲]]一間[[無國界醫生|無國界醫生]]醫院'''。事件發生在[[阿富汗|阿富汗]]北部[[昆都士省|昆都士省]][[昆都士|昆都士]]市。據報道空襲造成22人死亡，超過30人受傷，33人失蹤。<ref name="atlantic aftermath">{{cite news | url=http://www.theatlantic.com/international/archive/2015/10/doctors-without-borders-afghanistan-airstrike/408865/ | title=The Aftermath of the Airstrike on Doctors Without Borders | work=[[The_Atlantic|The Atlantic]] | date=2015-10-04 | accessdate=2015-10-04 | author=Wang, Amy X. | archive-date=2015-10-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151014042144/http://www.theatlantic.com/international/archive/2015/10/doctors-without-borders-afghanistan-airstrike/408865/ | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="cnn air attacks" /><ref name=NYT_Leaving>{{cite news|last1=Rubin|first1=Alissa J.|last2=Southall|first2=Ashley|title=Doctors Without Borders Says It Is Leaving Kunduz After Strike on Hospital|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/10/05/world/asia/doctors-without-borders-says-it-is-leaving-kunduz-after-strike-on-hospital.html?partner=rss&emc=rss&_r=0|accessdate=2015-10-05|work=The New York Times|date=2015-10-04|archive-date=2018-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180824135248/https://www.nytimes.com/2015/10/05/world/asia/doctors-without-borders-says-it-is-leaving-kunduz-after-strike-on-hospital.html?partner=rss&emc=rss&_r=0|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="The Guardian" />

無國界醫生嚴厲譴責這次事件，表示空襲發生前，交戰各方都已被告知醫院的位置，這次空襲是出於故意，違反[[國際人道法|國際人道法]]。<ref name="MSF statement">{{cite web|url=http://www.doctorswithoutborders.org/article/afghanistan-msf-demands-explanations-after-deadly-airstrikes-hit-hospital-kunduz|title=Afghanistan: MSF Demands Explanations After Deadly Airstrikes Hit Hospital in Kunduz|publisher=Doctors Without Borders|date=2015-10-03|accessdate=2015-10-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151006230131/http://www.doctorswithoutborders.org/article/afghanistan-msf-demands-explanations-after-deadly-airstrikes-hit-hospital-kunduz|archive-date=2015-10-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>[http://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/doctors-without-borders-deliberate-hospital-bombing_5613dca5e4b0368a1a6108dd Doctors Without Borders Enraged Over 'Deliberate' Kunduz Hospital Bombing] {{Wayback|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/doctors-without-borders-deliberate-hospital-bombing_5613dca5e4b0368a1a6108dd |date=20151009020022 }}. ''The Huffington Post,'' 6 October 2015.</ref>無國界醫生主席[[廖滿嫦|廖滿嫦]]譴責這次襲擊是「對[[日內瓦公約|日內瓦公約]]的攻擊」，呼籲獨立調查這次事件，宣佈尋求[[國際人道主義實況調查委員會|國際人道主義實況調查委員會]]啟動調查。<ref name="msf16641">{{cite web|url=http://msf.hk/news/16641|title=無國界醫生：即使戰爭也有規範|work=無國界醫生|date=2015-10-07|accessdate=2015-10-15|archive-date=2015-10-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151013153601/http://msf.hk/news/16641|dead-url=no}}</ref>

美國及北約駐阿富汗部隊司令[[約翰·坎貝爾_(美軍上將)|約翰·坎貝爾]]，其後證實美軍一架[[AC-130空中砲艇|AC-130空中砲艇]]曾襲擊醫院，又稱[[阿富汗軍隊|阿富汗軍隊]]遭到[[塔利班|塔利班]]襲擊而要求空襲，不符合較早前的講法。<ref name="WPost_struggles" /><ref name="NYT_requested">{{cite web | last=Rosenberg | first=Matthew | title=U.S. General Says Afghans Requested Airstrike That Hit Kunduz Hospital | website=The New York Times | date=2015-10-05 | url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/10/06/world/asia/afghanistan-kunduz-doctors-without-borders-hospital.html | accessdate=2015-10-06 | archive-date=2015-10-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151012205933/http://www.nytimes.com/2015/10/06/world/asia/afghanistan-kunduz-doctors-without-borders-hospital.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>[[美國|美國]]和[[北約|北約]]已展開事件調查。<ref name="npr">{{cite news | url=http://www.npr.org/sections/thetwo-way/2015/10/04/445773358/doctors-without-borders-kunduz-airstrike-was-war-crime | title=Doctors Without Borders: Kunduz Airstrike Was 'War Crime' | work=NPR | date=2015-10-04 | accessdate=2015-10-04 | archive-date=2015-10-10 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151010212152/http://www.npr.org/sections/thetwo-way/2015/10/04/445773358/doctors-without-borders-kunduz-airstrike-was-war-crime | dead-url=no }}</ref>2015年10月7日美國總統[[奧巴馬|奧巴馬]]為空襲道歉。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Shear|first1=Michael D.|last2=Sengupta|first2=Somini|title=Obama Issues Rare Apology Over Bombing of Doctors Without Borders Hospital in Afghanistan|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/10/08/world/asia/obama-apologizes-for-bombing-of-afghanistan-hospital.html?hp&action=click&pgtype=Homepage&module=a-lede-package-region&region=top-news&WT.nav=top-news&_r=0|accessdate=2015-10-08|work=The New York Times|date=2015-10-08|archive-date=2016-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160325155325/http://www.nytimes.com/2015/10/08/world/asia/obama-apologizes-for-bombing-of-afghanistan-hospital.html?hp&action=click&pgtype=Homepage&module=a-lede-package-region&region=top-news&WT.nav=top-news&_r=0|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2016年4月29日，美国国防部公布对2015年美军轰炸阿富汗“无国界医生”医院的军事调查结果，声称误炸“非故意”，所以不构成战争罪。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.guancha.cn/america/2016_04_30_358741.shtml |title=美国公布炸死阿富汗医院42人调查结果：无人面临起诉 |accessdate=2016-04-30 |archive-date=2016-05-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160502100630/http://www.guancha.cn/america/2016_04_30_358741.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>
==空襲事件==
===背景===
{{main|昆都士之戰}}
9月28日，[[塔利班|塔利班]]武裝佔據[[昆都士|昆都士]]，驅逐阿富汗政府軍出城。阿富汗陸軍隊在得到增援後，於美國空襲支援下反攻，經過幾日戰鬥，政府軍聲稱已經重奪城市，但是戰鬥仍然未完。

[[無國界醫生|無國界醫生]]已經告知交戰各方醫院建築物的位置。無國界醫生的人員最近一次是在9月29日，向美國軍官再次確認醫院準確位置的[[經緯度|經緯度]]。<ref name="dw-2015-10-03">{{Internetquelle|url=http://www.dw.com/de/us-angriff-auf-klinik-in-kundus-ein-kriegsverbrechen/a-18759857|titel=Afghanistan: US-Angriff auf Klinik in Kundus ein Kriegsverbrechen?|hrsg=Deutsche Welle|datum=2015-10-03|zugriff=2015-10-04}} {{Wayback|url=http://www.dw.com/de/us-angriff-auf-klinik-in-kundus-ein-kriegsverbrechen/a-18759857 |date=20151006015532 }}</ref>

===事件===
[[無國界醫生|無國界醫生]]表示，在當地時間10月3日凌晨02:08至03:15（[[UTC|UTC]]+04:30），組織在[[昆都士|昆都士]]的創傷醫院遭受到「一連串空襲轟炸」<ref name="msf16616">{{cite news|url=http://msf.hk/news/16616|title=阿富汗：昆都士醫院遭致命空襲後　無國界醫生要求解釋|work=無國界醫生|date=2015-10-04|accessdate=2015-10-13|archive-date=2015-10-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151013155709/http://msf.hk/news/16616|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="WPost_struggles">{{cite web | title=U.S. military struggles to explain how it wound up bombing Doctors Without Borders hospital | website=Washington Post | date=2015-10-05 | url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/checkpoint/wp/2015/10/05/afghan-forces-requested-airstrike-that-hit-hospital-in-kunduz/ | accessdate=2015-10-06 | archive-date=2015-10-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151015233859/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/checkpoint/wp/2015/10/05/afghan-forces-requested-airstrike-that-hit-hospital-in-kunduz/ | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="CNN_accidentally" />無國界醫生稱醫院在空襲中被「擊中幾次」，醫院大樓「有部份被炸毀」。<ref name="NYT_Airstrike"/>組織並指醫院被「重覆準確擊中」，即使組織員工在受襲時通知美國和阿富汗官員，但之後空襲依然持續三十分鐘。<ref name="CNN_dead">{{cite web | last=Rahim | first=Fazul | last2=Cumming | first2=Jason | last3=Sederholm | first3=Jillian | last4=Fieldstadt | first4=Elisha | title=19 Dead After Charity Hospital Hit by Apparent U.S. Airstrike | website=NBC News | date=2015-10-03 | url=http://www.nbcnews.com/news/world/16-dead-after-charity-hospital-hit-apparent-u-s-airstrike-n438001 | accessdate=2015-10-06 | archive-date=2015-10-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151016101329/http://www.nbcnews.com/news/world/16-dead-after-charity-hospital-hit-apparent-u-s-airstrike-n438001 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="BBC_disgust">{{cite web | title=Afghan conflict: MSF 'disgust' at government hospital claims | website=BBC News | date=2015-10-05 | url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-34440965 | accessdate=2015-10-06 | archive-date=2015-10-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151009203315/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-34440965 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

===事件確認和回應===
美國軍方最初聲稱，為了保護美軍地面安全部隊，在該地點作了一次空襲，及「可能對附近的醫療設施造成{{tsl|en|Collateral damage|附帶破壞}}」<ref name="NYT_Airstrike">{{cite web | last=Rubin | first=Alissa J. | title=Airstrike Hits Doctors Without Borders Hospital in Afghanistan | website=The New York Times | date=2015-10-03 | url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/10/04/world/asia/afghanistan-bombing-hospital-doctors-without-borders-kunduz.html | accessdate=2015-10-05 | archive-date=2015-10-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151014154007/http://www.nytimes.com/2015/10/04/world/asia/afghanistan-bombing-hospital-doctors-without-borders-kunduz.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>美國及北約駐阿富汗部隊司令[[約翰·坎貝爾_(美軍上將)|約翰·坎貝爾]]其後證實一架[[AC-130空中砲艇|AC-130空中砲艇]]作出決定攻擊醫院，回應遭受塔利班炮火攻擊的阿富汗軍隊的要求，與早前所言不符。<ref name="WPost_struggles"/><ref name="NYT_requested"/>他又明確指出使用空中火力的決定，是「在美國指揮系統內部作出」。<ref name="BBC_know"/>他指這次攻擊是「一個錯誤」，說「我們永不會蓄意以受保護的醫療設施為目標」。<ref name="BBC_mistake">{{cite web | title=Kunduz: Afghan MSF hospital strike a mistake, says US | website=BBC News | date=2015-10-07 | url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-34458270 | accessdate=2015-10-08 | archive-date=2015-10-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151009011710/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-34458270 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="dallasnews">{{cite news|url=http://www.dallasnews.com/news/local-news/20151006-top-us-commander-in-afghanistan-says-attack-on-hospital-was-a-mistake.ece|title=Top US commander in Afghanistan says attack on hospital was a mistake|website=The Dallas Morning News|date=2015-10-06|accessdate=2015-10-15|archive-date=2015-10-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151013040857/http://www.dallasnews.com/news/local-news/20151006-top-us-commander-in-afghanistan-says-attack-on-hospital-was-a-mistake.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref>白宮發言人[[约什·厄内斯特|约什·厄内斯特]]為美軍辯護，表示[[美國國防部|美國國防部]]比起世界上其他軍方「更加致力，更加注重避免平民傷亡」，又暗示美國或會賠償受害者及家屬。<ref name="CNN_accidentally"/><ref name="BBC_apologises"/>美國總統[[巴拉克·奧巴馬|巴拉克·奧巴馬]]為事件向無國界醫生組織主席[[廖滿嫦|廖滿嫦]]道歉，說這是一個錯誤，原本目標是塔利班戰士。<ref name="BBC_apologises">{{cite web | title=Obama apologises to MSF president for Kunduz bombing | website=BBC News | date=2015-10-07 | url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-34467631 | accessdate=2015-10-08 | archive-date=2015-10-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151015193528/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-34467631 | dead-url=no }}</ref>美國會向受害者及家屬發放「慰問金」（condolence payments）及出資重建醫院。<ref name="NPR_condolence">{{cite web | last=Peralta | first=Eyder | title=U.S. Will Make 'Condolence Payments' To Victims Of Kunduz Hospital Airstrike | website=NPR.org | date=2015-10-11 | url=http://www.npr.org/sections/thetwo-way/2015/10/11/447688399/u-s-will-make-condolence-payments-to-victims-of-kunduz-hospital-airstrike | accessdate=2015-10-14 | archive-date=2015-10-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151014015728/http://www.npr.org/sections/thetwo-way/2015/10/11/447688399/u-s-will-make-condolence-payments-to-victims-of-kunduz-hospital-airstrike | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="AP_orders"/>

{{tsl|en|Afghan Interior Ministry|阿富汗內政部}}發言人塞迪格·塞迪吉（Sediq Sediqi）證實10月3日的空襲，說「10至15名恐怖份子匿藏在醫院內」，又證實有醫院工作人員被殺。<ref name="Guardian_video">{{cite web | title=Afghan government confirms airstrike on Kunduz hospital – video | work=The Guardian | date=2015-10-05 | url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/video/2015/oct/03/afghan-government-confirms-airstrike-on-kunduz-hospital-video | accessdate=2015-10-05 | archive-date=2015-10-17 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151017014110/http://www.theguardian.com/world/video/2015/oct/03/afghan-government-confirms-airstrike-on-kunduz-hospital-video | dead-url=no }}</ref>{{tsl|en|Ministry of Defense (Afghanistan)|阿富汗國防部}}和昆都士警察總長的一名代表，也說塔利班戰士空襲時正藏身醫院內，該名代表聲稱這些人用醫院為{{tsl|en|human shield|人盾}}。<ref name="atlantic aftermath" /><ref name="cnn independent inquiry" />

[[無國界醫生|無國界醫生]]指當時醫院內沒有塔利班戰士，總幹事施托康（Christopher Stokes）在10月4日的聲明說：「對於有阿富汗政府部門最近正當化襲擊昆都士的醫院的言論，無國界醫生感到非常憤怒。這些說法暗示了阿富汗與美國軍隊一起決定要將這個全面運作中的醫院夷為平地──內有超過180名員工與病人──因為他們宣稱裡面有塔利班成員。這相當於承認[[戰爭犯罪|戰爭犯罪]]。」<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.latimes.com/world/afghanistan-pakistan/la-fg-doctors-without-borders-20151004-story.html |title=Doctors Without Borders closes Afghan hospital, says U.S. may have committed war crime |date=2015-10-04 |accessdate=2015-10-15 |archive-date=2015-10-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151015072259/http://www.latimes.com/world/afghanistan-pakistan/la-fg-doctors-without-borders-20151004-story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> <ref name="msf16623">{{cite web|url=http://msf.hk/news/16623|title=無國界醫生對合理化昆都士醫院襲擊的言論感到憤怒|work=無國界醫生|date=2015-10-05|accessdate=2015-10-15|archive-date=2015-10-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151013155652/http://msf.hk/news/16623|dead-url=no}}</ref>他說：「假如該處有重大軍事行動，我們的員工會注意到。而這並非空襲發生時的情況。」<ref name="cnn independent inquiry" />組織在10月5日發出聲明說：「他們（美國政府）不斷改變對這場襲擊的說法──從連帶傷害到悲痛事件，到現在試圖將責任轉嫁給阿富汗政府……這次令人震驚的襲擊沒有任何能夠正當化的理由。」<ref name="CNN_accidentally">{{cite web | last=Mullen | first=Jethro | last2=Fantz | first2=Ashley | title=Afghan hospital bombing: Civilians 'accidentally struck' | website=CNN | date=2015-10-05 | url=http://www.cnn.com/2015/10/05/asia/afghanistan-doctors-without-borders-hospital/index.html | accessdate=2015-10-06 | archive-date=2015-10-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151016073248/http://www.cnn.com/2015/10/05/asia/afghanistan-doctors-without-borders-hospital/index.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="msf16629">{{cite web|url=http://msf.hk/news/16629|title=無國界醫生就10月5日美國國防部聲明作出回應|work=無國界醫生|date=2015-10-05|accessdate=2015-10-15|archive-date=2015-10-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151013154256/http://msf.hk/news/16629|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===國際人道法===
[[國際人道法|國際人道法]]禁止攻擊醫療設施，除非該設施「越出其人道主義任務之外，用以從事有害於敵方之行為」。即使敵方武裝人員不正當地使用該設施作掩護，「攻擊中的比例性原則」通常禁止這種攻擊，因為很可能導致平民傷亡。戰爭法律要求攻擊者必須先作警告，等候合理時間回應，然後才可以攻擊被武裝人員不當使用的醫療單位。<ref name="BBC_know">{{cite web | title=Afghan conflict: What we know about Kunduz hospital bombing | website=BBC News | date=2015-10-07 | url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-34444053 | accessdate=2015-10-08 | archive-date=2015-10-07 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151007205057/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-34444053 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[[日內瓦公約|日內瓦第四公約]]第十八、十九條</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.icrc.org/chi/resources/documents/publication/pcustom.htm|title=習慣國際人道法|work=紅十字國際委員會|date=2005-03-07|accessdate=2015-10-14|archive-date=2016-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160115111746/http://www.icrc.org/chi/resources/documents/publication/pcustom.htm|dead-url=no}}第4章</ref>

==遇害者==
22名遇害者中，12人是[[無國界醫生|無國界醫生]]員工，10人是病人，包括3名兒童。6名深切治療病人在病床上燒死；另外，醫護被迫將病人留在手術床上，之後其中1名病人死亡。<ref name="cnn air attacks">{{cite news | url=http://www.cnn.com/2015/10/03/asia/afghanistan-doctors-without-borders-hospital/ | title=Air attacks kill at least 19 at Afghanistan hospital; U.S. investigating | publisher=CNN | date=2015-10-03 | accessdate=2015-10-04 | author=Popalzai, Masoud; Brumfield, Ben; Almasy, Steve and Jason Hanna | archive-date=2015-10-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151012083251/http://www.cnn.com/2015/10/03/asia/afghanistan-doctors-without-borders-hospital | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="ap leaves city">{{cite news | url=http://bigstory.ap.org/article/8508b50cad7141efaa442fffb3aba7a2/doctors-without-borders-leaves-afghan-city-after-airstrike | title=Doctors Without Borders leaves Afghan city after airstrike | work=AP | date=2015-10-04 | accessdate=2015-10-04 | author=O'Donnell, Lynne | archive-date=2015-10-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151005061201/http://bigstory.ap.org/article/8508b50cad7141efaa442fffb3aba7a2/doctors-without-borders-leaves-afghan-city-after-airstrike | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="nbc">{{cite news | url=http://www.nbcnews.com/news/world/16-dead-after-charity-hospital-hit-apparent-u-s-airstrike-n438001 | title=Doctors Without Borders Hospital in Kunduz Hit by Apparent U.S. Strike | work=NBC | date=2015-10-03 | accessdate=2015-10-04 | author=Rahim, Fazul; Cumming, Jason; Sederholm, Jillian; Fieldstadt, Elisha | archive-date=2015-10-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151016101329/http://www.nbcnews.com/news/world/16-dead-after-charity-hospital-hit-apparent-u-s-airstrike-n438001 | dead-url=no }}</ref>無國界醫生表示12名遇害員工都是阿富汗國民，在現場的全部3名外籍員工都生還。<ref name=NYT_Call_for_Inquiry>{{cite news|last=Cumming-Bruce|first=Nick|title=Doctors Without Borders Calls for Inquiry Into Kunduz Hospital Attack|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/10/08/world/europe/kunduz-afghanistan-hospital-doctors-without-borders.html|accessdate=2015-10-07|work=The New York Times|date=2015-10-07|archive-date=2015-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151010093708/http://www.nytimes.com/2015/10/08/world/europe/kunduz-afghanistan-hospital-doctors-without-borders.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>空襲後五日，無國界醫生表示，包括員工和病人在內，共有33人仍然失蹤。<ref name="The Guardian">{{cite web | url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/oct/09/msf-33-people-still-missing-us-airstrike-afghan-hospital | title=Doctors Without Borders airstrike: MSF says 33 people still missing | publisher=The Guardian | date=2015-10-08 | accessdate=2015-10-09 | archive-date=2015-10-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151013054210/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/oct/09/msf-33-people-still-missing-us-airstrike-afghan-hospital | dead-url=no }}</ref>

==撤離及關閉設施==
空襲使得醫院不能使用。所有重傷病人都轉送到其他醫療機構的醫院，[[無國界醫生|無國界醫生]]員工全都從[[昆都士|昆都士]]撤離。空襲之前，無國界醫生的醫院是當地惟一運作中的醫療設施。<ref name="atlantic aftermath" />這醫院是阿富汗東北部僅有的創傷醫院。2014年，這醫院治療超過二萬二千名病人，進行逾五千九百宗手術。<ref name="msf16616" />

當地時間10月15日下午，一輛美軍[[坦克|坦克]]闖入醫院，大門被坦克撞毀，似乎不知道無國界醫生的管理層人員正在醫院內，包括無國界醫生在阿富汗的國家代表莫利涅（Guilhem Molinie）。無國界醫生指：「他們不作事先通知就強行闖進醫院，損壞資產，破壞潛在證據，使我們團隊陷入緊張和恐慌。」他們被美軍告知坦克載着美國－北約－阿富汗調查人員。<ref>{{cite news|author1=Tom McCarthy|title=US tank enters ruined Afghan hospital putting 'war crime' evidence at risk|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/oct/15/us-tank-enters-ruined-afghan-hospital-putting-war-evidence-at-risk|accessdate=2015-10-20|work=The Guardian|date=2015-10-16|archive-date=2015-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151018114202/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/oct/15/us-tank-enters-ruined-afghan-hospital-putting-war-evidence-at-risk|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author1=KRISTA MAHR|title=MSF says U.S. tank entered compound of bombed Afghan hospital without permission|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/10/16/us-afghanistan-hospital-idUSKCN0SA1TQ20151016|accessdate=2015-10-20|work=Reuters|date=2015-10-16|archive-date=2015-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151019162758/http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/10/16/us-afghanistan-hospital-idUSKCN0SA1TQ20151016|dead-url=no}}</ref>雙方談判一個半小時後，無國界醫生人員容許對方入內，但是美軍士兵必須不攜帶武器。無國界醫生指先前與美國和阿富汗聯合調查組約定，調查過程中有任何行動牽涉到無國界醫生的人員或資產，無國界醫生都要得到事先知會。<ref>{{cite news|title=Kunduz: des soldats américains forcent l'entrée de l'hôpital de MSF bombardé|work=L'Express|url=http://www.lexpress.fr/actualite/monde/kunduz-des-soldats-americains-forcent-l-entree-de-l-hopital-de-msf-bombarde_1726496.html|date=2015-10-16|accessdate=2015-10-22|archive-date=2015-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151022062225/http://www.lexpress.fr/actualite/monde/kunduz-des-soldats-americains-forcent-l-entree-de-l-hopital-de-msf-bombarde_1726496.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|script-title=fr:Des militaires américains forcent l’entrée de l’hôpital de MSF à Kunduz|url=http://www.lemonde.fr/international/article/2015/10/16/des-militaires-americains-forcent-l-entree-de-l-hopital-de-msf-a-kunduz_4790957_3210.html|work=Le Monde|date=2015-10-16|accessdate=2015-10-22|archive-date=2015-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151018171232/http://www.lemonde.fr/international/article/2015/10/16/des-militaires-americains-forcent-l-entree-de-l-hopital-de-msf-a-kunduz_4790957_3210.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==調查==
北約、美國和阿富汗都展開了調查。美國總統[[巴拉克·奧巴馬|巴拉克·奧巴馬]]表示：「國防部已展開全面調查，我們會等候調查結果，再對事件情況下定論。……我……要求就事實和情況作出完整報告。」<ref name="cnn air attacks" /><ref name="npr"/>他並致以「最深切的慰問」。<ref name="atlantic aftermath" />美國駐阿富汗部隊司令[[約翰·坎貝爾_(美軍上將)|約翰·坎貝爾]]說：「我們現在正着手徹底調查事件，查明所發生的事，在此時我向受害者寄以哀思和禱告。……我們會一如既往地採取所有合理措施保護平民免受傷害。」<ref>{{Cite web| url = http://www.theguardian.com/world/live/2015/oct/03/msf-staff-killed-in-suspected-us-strike-on-afghan-hospital-latest| title = US and Afghanistan vow investigation into air strike on MSF hospital – as it happened| first = Jaime| last = Grierson| first2 = Oliver| last2 = Duggan| work = The Guardian| date = 2015-10-03| accessdate = 2015-10-05| archive-date = 2015-10-15| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151015223233/http://www.theguardian.com/world/live/2015/oct/03/msf-staff-killed-in-suspected-us-strike-on-afghan-hospital-latest| dead-url = no}}</ref>美國官員表示美國陸軍准將理查德•金（Richard Kim）會領導調查；其他兩個調查，一個由北約進行，一個由美軍與阿富汗安全官員進行。<ref name="Reuters_called">{{cite web | last=Torbati | first=Yeganeh | title=Afghan forces called for air strike in Kunduz: U.S. general | website=Reuters | date=2015-10-06 | url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/10/06/us-afghanistan-attack-usa-idUSKCN0RZ1FX20151006 | accessdate=2015-10-06 | archive-date=2015-10-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151014023908/http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/10/06/us-afghanistan-attack-usa-idUSKCN0RZ1FX20151006 | dead-url=no }}</ref>[[阿富汗總統|阿富汗總統]][[阿什拉夫·加尼·艾哈邁德扎伊|阿什拉夫·加尼·艾哈邁德扎伊]]委任五人小組，調查這次空襲及[[昆都士之戰|昆都士之戰]]。<ref name="AP_orders">{{cite web | author=The Associated Press | title=Afghan President Orders Investigation Into Fall of Kunduz | website= | date=2015-10-10 | url=http://www.nytimes.com/aponline/2015/10/10/world/asia/ap-as-afghanistan.html | accessdate=2015-10-14 | archive-date=2015-10-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151013064425/http://www.nytimes.com/aponline/2015/10/10/world/asia/ap-as-afghanistan.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>

[[無國界醫生|無國界醫生]]呼籲應該對空襲醫院作獨立調查。總幹事施托康說：「我們需要一個儘可能獨立和透明的調查。我們不只要調查結果公開，我們還要能夠讀到完整報告。」<ref name="cnn independent inquiry">{{cite news | url=http://www.cnn.com/2015/10/04/asia/afghanistan-doctors-without-borders-hospital/ | title=Medical charity urges independent inquiry after Afghan hospital blown apart | publisher=CNN | date=2015-10-04 | accessdate=2015-10-04 | author=Popalzai, Masoud; Brumfield, Ben; Almasy, Steve and Jason Hanna | archive-date=2015-10-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151009191935/http://www.cnn.com/2015/10/04/asia/afghanistan-doctors-without-borders-hospital/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>他又說：「依賴於交戰的一方所作的內部調查是全然不足夠的。……基於戰爭罪行已被犯下的明顯推定，無國界醫生要求由獨立國際組織，進行全面和透明的事件調查。」<ref name="reuters medical charity">{{cite news | url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/10/04/us-afghanistan-attack-idUSKCN0RW0HC20151004 | title=Medical charity MSF demands independent inquiry into air strike on Afghan hospital | work=Reuters | date=2015-10-04 | accessdate=2015-10-04 | author=Harooni, Mirwais and Andrew MacAskill | archive-date=2015-10-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151005054224/http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/10/04/us-afghanistan-attack-idUSKCN0RW0HC20151004 | dead-url=no }}</ref>坎貝爾說若有需要，美國陸軍會「協調」其他調查。<ref name="Reuters_called" />無國界醫生組織指明，獨立調查應該交由[[國際人道主義實況調查委員會|國際人道主義實況調查委員會]]進行。<ref name="">{{Internetquelle | url=http://www.independent.ie/world-news/independent-factfinding-mission-urged-over-deadly-kunduz-strike-31590275.html | titel=Independent fact-finding mission urged over deadly Kunduz strike - Independent.ie | titelerg= | autor= | hrsg= | werk= | seiten= | datum=7 October 2015 | zugriff=8 October 2015 | sprache= | kommentar= | zitat= | offline= }} {{Wayback|url=http://www.independent.ie/world-news/independent-factfinding-mission-urged-over-deadly-kunduz-strike-31590275.html |date=20151126053756 }}</ref>主席[[廖滿嫦|廖滿嫦]]宣佈已請求啟動該調查委員會，因為這是「唯一為調查違反國際人道法的情形而專門設立的永久團體」。這個委員會成立於1991年，總部位於[[伯恩|伯恩]]，根據[[日內瓦公約|日內瓦公約]]第一附加議定書而設立，此前從來未啟動過。<ref name="msf16641" />

[[聯合國人權事務高級專員|聯合國人權事務高級專員]]{{tsl|en|Zeid Ra'ad Al Hussein|扎伊德·拉阿德·侯賽因}}也要求作出調查。他說：「這次事件是徹底的悲慘，不可原諒，更可能涉及罪行。國際及阿富汗軍事謀劃者有義務無論何時都尊重和保護平民，而醫療設施和人員是特別保護對象。」<ref name="UN tragic">{{cite web | url=http://www.un.org/apps/news/story.asp?NewsID=52164 | title=Afghanistan: UN strongly condemns 'tragic, inexcusable' Kunduz hospital airstrike | publisher=UN | accessdate=2015-10-04 | archive-date=2015-10-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151013150536/http://www.un.org/apps/news/story.asp?NewsID=52164 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

